"title": "5932: response",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5932: response",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>People are to respond to God in obedience, worship and repentance and in love for others. Lack of response from others can be a sign of death, disobedience and defiance.</p>\n<h2>The response of people to God</h2>\n<h3>Obedience and love for others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:3\">EXO 24:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:11\">1JN 4:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:8\">EXO 19:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:7\">EXO 24:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:6-1Chr29:9\">1CH 29:6–29:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:7\">ROM 15:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:2\">GAL 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:1-Phil2:4\">PHP 2:1–2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:3-1John2:6\">1JN 2:3–2:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:16-1John3:17\">1JN 3:16–3:17</a></p>\n<h3>Worship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh8:6\">NEH 8:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1\">ROM 12:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh12:24\">NEH 12:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:34-Dan4:37\">DAN 4:34–4:37</a></p>\n<h3>Repentance</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:18-2Kgs22:20\">2KI 22:18–22:20</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:26-2Chr34:28\">2CH 34:26–34:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:37-Acts2:38\">ACT 2:37–2:38</a></p>\n<h3>Response to the preaching of the gospel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:14\">ACT 16:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:31-Acts16:34\">ACT 16:31–16:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:1-1Cor15:2\">1CO 15:1–15:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:13\">EPH 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:6\">COL 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:13\">1TH 2:13</a></p>\n<h3>Inappropriate responses</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:24-2Chr32:25\">2CH 32:24–32:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:24-Dan4:32\">DAN 4:24–4:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:21-Rom1:23\">ROM 1:21–1:23</a></p>\n<h2>The response of God to people</h2>\n<h3>God responds to those who seek him in prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:17\">PSA 102:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps3:4\">PSA 3:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:1-Ps40:3\">PSA 40:1–40:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:22\">ISA 19:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:12\">DAN 10:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:7-Matt7:11\">MAT 7:7–7:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:9-Luke11:13\">LUK 11:9–11:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:5-Luke11:8\">LUK 11:5–11:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:13-John14:14\">JHN 14:13–14:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:7\">JHN 15:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:24\">JHN 16:24</a></p>\n<h3>Sometimes God appears not to respond to prayer</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:7\">JOB 19:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:1\">PSA 10:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps13:1-Ps13:2\">PSA 13:1–13:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:1-Ps22:2\">PSA 22:1–22:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:9-Ps42:10\">PSA 42:9–42:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:15\">ISA 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:1-Isa59:2\">ISA 59:1–59:2</a></p>\n<h2>False gods do not respond to people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:26-1Kgs18:29\">1KI 18:26–18:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:28\">DEU 4:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:18\">ISA 44:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:5\">JER 10:5</a></p>\n<h2>The response of people to others</h2>\n<h3>Believers should respond to others in kindness and forgiveness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:32\">EPH 4:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen50:15\">GEN 50:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen50:21\">GEN 50:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:38-Matt5:42\">MAT 5:38–5:42</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:29-Luke6:30\">LUK 6:29–6:30</a></p>\n<h3>Harsh or aggressive responses</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam19:43\">2SA 19:43</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:19-Rom12:21\">ROM 12:19–12:21</a></p>\n<h2>Lack of response</h2>\n<h3>As an indication of death</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam4:20\">1SA 4:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:31\">2KI 4:31</a></p>\n<h3>As a sign of disobedience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:27-Jer7:29\">JER 7:27–7:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:19\">PRO 29:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:30\">JER 2:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:23\">JER 17:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:33\">JER 32:33</a></p>\n<h3>As a sign of defiance</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:36\">2KI 18:36</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa36:21\">ISA 36:21</a></p>\n<h3>From not knowing what to say</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job32:15-Job32:16\">JOB 32:15–32:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job40:3-Job40:5\">JOB 40:3–40:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:46\">MAT 22:46</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:26\">LUK 20:26</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ made no response at his trial</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:14\">MAT 27:14</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:5\">MRK 15:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:61\">MRK 14:61</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:22-1Pet2:23\">1PE 2:22–2:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:9\">ISA 53:9</a></p>",
